  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">A novel approach for generating giant electronic persistent currents in symmetric defect mesoscopic-ring networks</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
